sections.Trivia:
- Masaru Miyadai wears a shirt showing the logo of the "Tokyo Spirits".
- The names of the suspects are related to department stores[1]:
- Ujiyasu Hosogoe (細越 氏康) comes from the chain Sogo (そごう, Sogō);
- Takashi Kamaya (鎌屋 崇司) comes from the chain Takashimaya (髙島屋);
- Mitsuko Shikama (鹿間 充子) comes from the chain Mitsukoshi (三越);
- Masaru Miyadai (宮台 優) comes from the chain Daimaru (大丸).
